<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870729-0162 </DOCNO><HL> Correction</HL><DD> 07/29/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><TEXT>   Yesterday's Leisure andamp; Arts page article on Jim Lehrer misidentified his father. He was a bus-company employee, not a bus driver.    (See: &quot;LEISURE andamp; ARTS: Author, Author: Jim Lehrer's Busman's Holiday&quot; -- WSJ July 28, 1987) </TEXT></DOC>